@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="static-page">
    <div class="static-page-header">
        <h1 class="page-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="page-subtitle">Last updated: January 2026</p>
    </div>

    <div class="static-content">

        <div class="static-block">
            <h2>1. Who We Are</h2>
            <p>GLH (Gloucestershire Local Hub) is a local food marketplace connecting communities with independent food producers across Gloucestershire and the surrounding regions. We are committed to protecting your personal data and being transparent about how we use it.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="static-block">
            <h2>2. What Data We Collect</h2>
            <p>We collect the following types of personal data when you use our platform:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Account information</strong> — your email address and password when you register</li>
                <li><strong>Order information</strong> — delivery address, items purchased, and payment records</li>
                <li><strong>Usage data</strong> — pages visited, products viewed, and basket activity</li>
                <li><strong>Communications</strong> — any messages you send to us or to producers through the platform</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="static-block">
            <h2>3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
            <p>Your data is used to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Process and fulfil your orders</li>
                <li>Manage your account and loyalty points</li>
                <li>Send order confirmations and updates</li>
                <li>Improve our platform and personalise your experience</li>
                <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="static-block">
            <h2>4. Who We Share Your Data With</h2>
            <p>We share relevant order information (such as your name and delivery address) with the producers fulfilling your order. We do not sell your personal data to third parties. We may share data with trusted service providers who assist in operating our platform, subject to confidentiality agreements.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="static-block">
            <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
            <p>We retain your account data for as long as your account is active. Order records are kept for up to 7 years for legal and accounting purposes. You may request deletion of your account and associated data at any time by contacting us.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="static-block">
            <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
            <p>Under UK GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
                <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
                <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
                <li>Object to or restrict certain processing</li>
                <li>Data portability</li>
            </ul>
            <p>To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@glh.co.uk">hello@glh.co.uk</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="static-block">
            <h2>7. Cookies</h2>
            <p>We use essential cookies to keep you logged in and maintain your basket session. We do not use advertising or tracking cookies. You can manage cookie preferences through your browser settings.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="static-block">
            <h2>8. Contact</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions about this policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@glh.co.uk">hello@glh.co.uk</a> or write to us at GLH, Cheltenham, Gloucestershire.</p>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>